plaza hotel cited reagans steadfast friendship for the jewish 
people and vehement rejection of antisemitism 
in recent weeks reagan has been honored by the american jewish 
committee and hebrew university in a few weeks he will be feted 
by the united jewish appeal drive 
reagan joked to the appreciative blacktie audience that his 
receipt of the honorary doctor of philosophy degree cannot be 
based on any academic achievements 
he went on to explain that his alma mater eureka college in 
illinois once gave him an honorary degree 25 years after his 
graduation 
that only aggravated a sense of guilt that i nursed for 25 
years reagan said i always suspected the first degree was 
honorary 
