newly reelected prime minister toshiki kaifu today 
formed a new cabinet after hours of factional wrangling and 
succeeded in keeping out scandaltainted politicians 
the backstage maneuvering followed parliaments vote earlier 
tday to leave the prime ministers post with kaifu who led his 
