to extricate the vessel it didnt matter because the engine was not 
powerful enough move it the 450 feet required to get off the reef 
do you know how much thrust would have to be generated by the 
engine to move this vessel one inch asked chalos 
no said greiner theres no way to calculate it 
chalos then asked whether after the accident the ship was 
capable of moving even one inch 
obviously it wasnt said greiner it didnt move 
